taxonomy_context.module
INSTALL

Requirements
------------

This module requires Drupal 4.5 RC or later.

Installation
------------

This module requires no modification to the Drupal database.

1. Create a new directory "taxonomy_context" in the modules/ directory
   and copy there:
   * taxonomy_context.module
   * taxonomy_context.css
   * the images directory together with its content (two image files).

2. Go to administration > settings > modules in the administration 
   pages and enable the module.

3. Check the "settings" page and set the module settings to your liking.

See README.txt for more details.

